title: This Week - S13E16 - 2015.01.22 - 468p x264
description:
POLITICAL: This Week
On: BBC 1 HD 
Date: Thursday 22nd January 2015 
Time: 23:35 to 00:20 

Andrew Neil reviews the political week with Alan Johnson, Michael Portillo, 
Caroline Lucas and Miranda Green. Glamour model Laura Lacole tells why she 
disagrees with the Sun's decision to drop its Page Three pictures. Isabel 
Oakeshott rounds up the political week in a film. Brendan Cole from Strictly 
Come Dancing discusses criticism, and how people respond to it. Crack open the 
Blue Nun and prepare to watch public service broadcasting at its best.
